text: Miloš Kolejka (born 18 October 1926) is a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
